Germany’s Scholz Wants to Ban National Party, Abendblatt Reports

-- B y   R a g n h i l d   K j e t l a n d
-- 
2011-07-25T05:31:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/germany-s-scholz-wants-to-ban-national-party-abendblatt-reports.html
Germany ’s National Democratic Party
should be banned because of its extremist views according to
Social Democratic Party vice chairman Olaf Scholz, the Hamburger
 Abendblatt  reported.  Scholz, a former Labor Minister in German Chancellor Angela Merkel’s first-term government, said the NPD isn’t
“compatible” with Germany’s constitution, the newspaper
reported, according to an e-mailed preview of an article that
will appear in today’s edition.  To contact the reporter on this story: Ragnhild Kjetland in
Frankfurt at   rkjetland@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong in Berlin at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  